            <title>[LU-18787] sanity-hsm test 12u fails for ZFS 2.3.0</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18787</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With Oleg&apos;s debug kernel setup we are seeing san-ty-hsm 12u failing.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;== sanity-hsm test 12u: Multiple reads on multiple HSM imported files in parallel ========================================================== 08:43:13 (1741441393) Starting copytool &apos;agt1&apos; on &apos;oleg604-client.virtnet&apos; with cmdline &apos;lhsmtool_posix --archive-format=v2 --hsm-root=/tmp/arc1/sanity-hsm.test_12u/ --daemon --pid-file=/var/run/lhsmtool_posix.pid &quot;/mnt/lustre2&quot;&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Waiting 200s for &apos;SUCCEED&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Waiting 190s for &apos;SUCCEED&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Waiting 180s for &apos;SUCCEED&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Waiting 80s for &apos;SUCCEED&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Waiting 20s for &apos;SUCCEED&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Update not seen after 200s: want &apos;SUCCEED&apos; got &apos;&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity-hsm test_12u: @@@@@@ FAIL: request on 0x200000403:0x34:0x0 is not SUCCEED on mds1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
